import React from 'react'
import { 
    Wrapper,
    Container,
    InputsContainer,
    SearchInput,
    FilterSelect, } from '../HomePage/style'
function HomePage() {
    return (
       <Wrapper>
           <Container className ='container'>
                <InputsContainer>
                    <SearchInput/>
                    <FilterSelect>

                    </FilterSelect>
                </InputsContainer>
           </Container>
       </Wrapper>
    )
}

export default HomePage
